{"tid":1592623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「香港全民議政會」(HK Assembly) Logo投票","createTime":"2019-09-24T16:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T05:49:58.000Z","uid":300718,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"223a9a9f03a4ed9645e0b12784c6fb5e6c162b9a","tid":1592623,"uid":300718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:44:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">HK Assembly Logo投票Link：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=29519fd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vyTs8Wx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvyTs8Wx.jpg&h=306d0b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;關於Logo投票&gt;</span></span><br />\nHK Assembly成立的目的，不單是讓全港市民議論政事，更希望建立民主平台，讓全民以公投方式發聲，同時將平台民主制度完善，成為能與政制競爭的類政制。<br />\n但是在達到理想前，必須逐步累積技術和經驗。因此，我們決定對投票機制進行第一次測試，以現階段盡量民主的方式讓大家選出共同的「香港全民議政會」Logo。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;投票機制&gt;</span></span><br />\n投票採用兩輪的簡單多數制。最高票數的兩款將交由設計師作最後加工，在第二輛投票獲較高票數的一款將成為 HK Assembly 的官方 Logo。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">規則：</span></span><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: violet;\">一人一票</span> [1] <br />\n2. 第一輪投票時間：<span style=\"color: violet;\">24/9 11PM - 26/9 11PM</span> （香港時間，共48小時）[2]<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: violet;\">以「香港全民議政會」投票及發佈Channel投票：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=29519fd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a> [3]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">投票需要你：</span></span><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: violet;\">加入Channel：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=29519fd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: violet;\">投票</span><br />\n3. <span style=\"color: violet;\">叫朋友</span>加入Channel一起投票！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&lt;感謝支持&gt;</span></span><br />\n集合全港多名設計精英，文宣組共設計了七款 Logo，在此先向這些有心人<span style=\"color: violet;\">致謝</span>。<br />\n希望藉著這次投票，和大家一起開始建立<span style=\"color: violet;\">真正屬於香港人的民主議政平台</span>。<br />\n隨人數增加、平台民主及身份認證制度變得完善，希望HK Assembly將變得更具公信力，讓大家<span style=\"color: violet;\">投票救港</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">HK Assembly Logo投票Link：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=29519fd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n- - - - - - - - - -<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">隨意門：《香港全民議政會》 HK Assembly 正式成立 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1590386/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1590386/page/1</a><br />\n- - - - - - - - - -<br />\n[1] 暫時未有機制解決Telegram上一人多號引致一人多票的身份認證問題，但：<br />\n1. 這是初期階段未能解決的複雜問題<br />\n2. 估計一人多號佔使用者比例不高<br />\n3. 因為抵消效果，減少對投票結果影響<br />\n4. 對此投票問題，控制投票結果的誘因不大<br />\n[2] 兩款設計交由設計師作最後加工後，第二輛投票預計於29/9進行<br />\n[3]<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 無Telegram？【趁而家快D裝啦！】</span></span>隨人數增加、平台民主及身份認證制度變得完善，希望HK Assembly將變得更具公信力，讓大家投票救港！"},{"pid":"792518b67a046990460c43ec4433098cd0221b22","tid":1592623,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"81aec6591f71951a944cbcecd4e5f8a09db840a3","tid":1592623,"uid":220045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:47:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e50cefbd9b7a9431ba3e2ab56813dd2301496f3","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:48:42.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb236b8f3035bf814e456033a0b8792adfe9c5f6","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:48:53.000Z","msg":"十連"},{"pid":"d1ea3590665b1e18b62a129aa232cdf7d71b3465","tid":1592623,"uid":74076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1773dabde3cd4af2b04e6b44cb7ae5e0004a9e5","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb236b8f3035bf814e456033a0b8792adfe9c5f6","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:48:53.000Z","msg":"十連"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:49:04.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2e8f0cf954ca11943cd33295f0a4e5bc71726d7a","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1773dabde3cd4af2b04e6b44cb7ae5e0004a9e5","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb236b8f3035bf814e456033a0b8792adfe9c5f6","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score