 /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105736e754f3c28cc9e6a1f031a438df5111ee2b","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />come and vote"},{"pid":"2e89cdca44dad7c213a4beddef18f7b1bf94717a","tid":1592623,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376294dc8c1c989a8d0c0eb4645673763396f966","tid":1592623,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:54:33.000Z","msg":"your vote counts <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1066cc080c0d421c5f6dce5c3d81b3c5e702829d","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:55:11.000Z","msg":"&lt;關於Logo投票&gt;<br />\nHK Assembly成立的目的，不單是讓全港市民議論政事，更希望建立民主平台，讓全民以公投方式發聲，同時將平台民主制度完善，成為能與政制競爭的類政制。<br />\n但是在達到理想前，必須逐步累積技術和經驗。因此，我們決定對投票機制進行第一次測試，以現階段盡量民主的方式讓大家選出共同的「香港全民議政會」Logo。"},{"pid":"93f3ed96a61851082e23c0af987bccf710d19987","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"&lt;投票機制&gt;<br />\n投票採用兩輪的簡單多數制。最高票數的兩款將交由設計師作最後加工，在第二輛投票獲較高票數的一款將成為 HK Assembly 的官方 Logo。"},{"pid":"1d70cf8eccc3c07a180941a8f040775fe0ec93a2","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:55:41.000Z","msg":"規則：<br />\n1. 一人一票 [1]<br />\n2. 第一輪投票時間：24/9 11PM - 26/9 11PM （香港時間，共48小時）[2]<br />\n3. 以「香港全民議政會」投票及發佈Channel投票： <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=29519fd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a> [3]"},{"pid":"ae522e9f4dbf6036bd7f6a979e6a017adff7bd7b","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:55:54.000Z","msg":"投票需要你：<br />\n1. 加入Channel： <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=29519fd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n2. 投票<br />\n3. 叫朋友加入Channel一起投票！"},{"pid":"e1183493ff11eba5ea90d87629c453ca0699d85c","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:56:04.000Z","msg":"&lt;感謝支持&gt;<br />\n集合全港多名設計精英，文宣組共設計了七款 Logo，在此先向這些有心人致謝。<br />\n希望藉著這次投票，和大家一起開始建立真正屬於香港人的民主議政平台。<br />\n隨人數增加、平台民主及身份認證制度變得完善，希望HK Assembly將變得更具公信力，讓大家投票救港！"},{"pid":"6a63ee6e1237ad944cb1d05dce801a40f9ae725a","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"HK Assembly Logo投票Link： <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=29519fd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n- - - - - - - - - -<br />\n隨意門：《香港全民議政會》 HK Assembly 正式成立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1590386/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1590386/page/1</a><br />\n- - - - - - - - - -"},{"pid":"926136a6c37213cc6381766d915cd69e66d2baa9","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:56:26.000Z","msg":"[1] 暫時未有機制解決Telegram上一人多號引致一人多票的身份認證問題，但：<br />\n1. 這是初期階段未能解決的複雜問題<br />\n2. 估計一人多號佔使用者比例不高<br />\n3. 因為抵消效果，減少對投票結果影響<br />\n4. 對此投票問題，控制投票結果的誘因不大<br />\n[2] 兩款設計交由設計師作最後加工後，第二輛投票預計於29/9進行<br />\n[3] 無Telegram？【趁而家快D裝啦！】隨人數增加、平台民主及身份認證制度變得完善，希望HK Assembly將變得更具公信力，讓大家投票救港！"},{"pid":"88adac84973c388573032d991e007937990a689b","tid":1592623,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:56:51.000Z","msg":"[突發]930三罷 文宣工作立即開始!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592295</a>"},{"pid":"aa5536318dbbb0d8d149e6bf3485ee4e60ec6993","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />投票呀"},{"pid":"0fe9886dfc35b7f2d8d38ae90b142f57c5e30e99","tid":1592623,"uid":169361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:06:07.000Z","msg":"無個投得落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋設計呢啲嘢唔識合搞投票㗎"},{"pid":"14488c785990f286a01dacc2ab4198698932cb6c","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:08:54.000Z","msg":"認真post 無人推？"},{"pid":"0e7caa831c1ef257b6532fed0caa2f88491248aa","tid":1592623,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fe9886dfc35b7f2d8d38ae90b142f57c5e30e99","tid":1592623,"uid":169361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:06:07.000Z","msg":"無個投得落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />